<p>And now we're stuck... we don't have the return value from <code>shell_exec()</code> above. Good news,
there is a really nice trick for this. Whenever you need to share data between functions
in <code>FeatureContext</code>, you'll just create a new private property. At the top of the class
let's create a <code>private $output</code> property and update the <code>iRun</code> function to
<code>$this-&gt;output = shell_exec($command);</code>:</p>
